data.description: Just listed this adorable 2 bedroom ranch in Marlington Schools!  Don't miss this opportunity to get settled into your new home before the holidays! Pack your boxes and move right in.  All appliances are included, with a stove, refrigerator, dishwasher, and microwave.  Washer and Dryer hookups in the full basement.  And a nice yard with a newer oversized shed great for woodworking and hobby shop! Call today!
